'''Arraxx''' was a [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] who flew a [[Z-95 Headhunter/Legends|Z-95 Headhunter]] in the [[Eskaron]] races for [[Nirama]].

In [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]], during one race in which Arraxx was winning, Arraxx's path crossed with that of [[Gael Kinner]], who was flying in a separate private race. To avoid a collision, Kinner blasted Arraxx's Z-95 Headhunter into a cloud of debris. This [[Death/Legends|killed]] Arraxx and earned Kinner Nirama's wrath.

